gzip --> Lempel-Ziv
bzip2 --> Burrows-Wheeler
xz --> Lemple-Ziv-Markov (LZMA)
===========================================================================

Archiving:
	- Create
		> tar -c [-f ARCHIVE] [OPTIONS] [FILE...]
		> -z --> gzip compression
		> -j --> bzip2 compression
	- List
		> tar -t [-f ARCHIVE] [OPTIONS]
	- Extract
		> tar -x [-f ARCHIVE] [OPTIONS]
===========================================================================

zip [OPTIONS] [zipfile [fileâ€¦]]
	> creates archive
	> -r --> recursion

unzip 
	> -l --> list
